abstract: Liz Cheney’s early purchase of a resident fishing license in Wyoming has inflamed her critics in the state, who have already accused her of being an interloper who should not dare challenge Senator Michael B. Enzi in next year’s Republican primary.

headline.main: Fishing License Becomes Issue for Liz Cheney in Wyoming Senate Race
